{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Blast, Upgrade, and Adapt in this fast-paced roguelike shooter!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Bodacious Blasteroids</strong> is a high octane arcade shooter where firepower is everything. Build an arsenal of devastating weapons and obliterate waves of evolving enemies. But there\u2019s a catch. Your guns overheat, forcing you to rotate between weapons on the fly. Master the art of swapping weapons to unleash devastating combos!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501600/extras/steam_gif_2.gif?t=1739880873\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Rotating Firepower</strong> \u2013 Stay on your toes! Your weapons overheat, so be prepared to switch up tactics constantly. Find the ultimate synergy between your tools of destruction as you swap your way to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501600/extras/ezgif-354d4623d649a6.gif?t=1739880873\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Evolving Arsenal</strong> \u2013 Upgrade your weapons in wild ways! Stack mods  to transform your weapons into a screen-clearing powerhouses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3501600/extras/steam_gif_3.gif?t=1739880873\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Adaptive Enemies</strong> \u2013 You're not the only one getting stronger. Enemies evolve, gaining new skills and attack patterns...\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Hope you've got the skills, 'cause you're gonna need them...</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/st